title: Biden administration tells Supreme Court to block Texas social media law
description: Prelogar’s response clears the way for the Supreme Court to take up the state social media law cases in the next term.

title: What to do when you’re accused of AI cheating
description: AI writing detectors like Turnitin and GPTZero suffer from false positives. Here’s the advice of academics, AI scientists and students on how to deal with it.
